<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
	This file enables the definition of the flexbom of a specific project/product.
  Below we show a set of possible valid values.
  
  Bucket matrix path (FULL_UNC_PATH_TO_BUCKET_MATRIX_REVISION)
	-> The bucket matrix path should be a full unc path referencing an existing location in the lava export
     Example:
			 * \\amr.corp.intel.com\ec\proj\mpe\Lava\Production\Releases\GNR_UCC_XCC\BucketMatrix\Bucketing_UCC_XCC_GROUP_Dummy\Release V1.0.0
      
  Hri (HRI_VALUE)
  -> A 12 characters HRI with no spaces and a comma separated value list of boms.
     Example:
       * GNRUCCXCC123
       
  Boms (BOMS_ASSOCIATED)
  -> A comma separated list of boms.
     Example:
      * NE4QCNCV_E,NE4QCNRV_E
      * all
      
  Enabled Bins:
  -> One or more enabled bins for a specific HRI. <allEnabled> can be used just one and without any other enabled bins defined. The olb_bin is the one from bucket matrix.
     Example: 
      <enabled olb_bin ="1"/>
      <allEnabled/>
-->
